Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.89,0:22:12.40,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HFFAE04&\blur3}It’s been always something cruel, dark and sore
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.40,0:22:17.03,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HACD837&\blur3}Chikazuku dabi kirameku tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.03,0:22:21.07,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HACD837&\blur3}Konomune oshiyoseru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:25.05,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HDB2594&\blur3}Ureshii demo kurushii
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:29.41,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HDB2594&\blur3}Koko kara saki wa muri ni chikazukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:34.09,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Yasashii koe de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.09,0:22:38.37,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Tada kono mama de itai dake
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:42.68,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Yusaburanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:45.85,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Na no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:54.97,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Daremo kuzusenai kizukiageta barikeedo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:23:08.00,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Kataku tozashiteta hazu datta no ni doushite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.00,0:23:21.76,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Do you hear weary heart’s S.O.S.?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:22:03.89,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HFFAE04&\blur3}Foi algo agradável e doce... até que ganhei juízo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.89,0:22:12.40,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HFFAE04&\blur3}Sempre foi algo cruel, escuro e doloroso
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.40,0:22:17.03,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HACD837&\blur3}Toda vez que eu me aproximo... toda vez que eu brilho
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.03,0:22:21.07,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HACD837&\blur3}meu peito começa a acelerar
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:25.05,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HDB2594&\blur3}Estou feliz, mas dói
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:29.41,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HDB2594&\blur3}De agora em diante, eu não deveria me forçar
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:34.09,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Mas diga com uma voz mais suave...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.09,0:22:38.37,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Eu só quero ficar assim
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:42.68,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Não me force assim...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:45.85,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Porém...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:54.97,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Era para ser uma fortaleza que ninguém iria penetrar
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:23:08.00,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Deveria ser impenetrável, mas por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.00,0:23:21.76,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Você ouve o chamado de emergência deste coração?
